{
  "id": "adv_group_moon_04_03",
  "title": "月のテンペスト 04 03",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagasektnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagasektnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――事故からしばらく経って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Some time after the accident…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん、体調はどう？\nずっと休んでるけど、まだ学校に行くのは無理そう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan‚ how are you feeling?\nYou've been resting for a while‚ is it still too hard to go to school?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagasektnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagasektnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 11.0502952297
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "ごめん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Sorry…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.0502952297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagasektnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagasektnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 13.0132428487
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "そっか……でも、きっとすぐ元気になれるよ\nそしたらまた二人で楽しいことを一杯しようよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… But you'll definitely be okay soon.\nAnd then we can do lots of fun things together again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagasektnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagasektnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 23.6374372164
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "無理よ……\nお姉ちゃんにもう会えないのに、元気になんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's impossible…\nHow can I be okay when I can't see my sister anymore…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.6952607631,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagasektnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagasektnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 32.3125622749
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "無理じゃないよ。今は辛いかもしれないけど\n琴乃ちゃんなら、きっとすぐに――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not impossible. It might be tough now‚\nbut I'm sure you'll be fine soon‚ Kotono-chan――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagasektnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagasektnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 38.7026322681
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "無理なの！　私は自分が許せないの！\nお姉ちゃんを忘れて元気になんてなれない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it's impossible! I can't forgive myself!\nI can't forget about my sister and be okay…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.9623828569,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagasektnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagasektnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 50.611974875
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "許せないって……\n麻奈さんのことは琴乃ちゃんのせいじゃないよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You can't forgive yourself…?\nIt wasn't your fault‚ Kotono-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.311974875,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagasektnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagasektnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 58.4559887566
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "分かってる……分かってるけど……\n私、お姉ちゃんに酷いことを言ったのよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know… I know‚ but…\nI… I said something horrible to my sister…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.1101153531,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagasektnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagasektnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 69.7928117749
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "酷いこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Horrible things?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.7928117749,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagaseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "nagaseliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.9429720279
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagaseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "nagaseliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.9429720279
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんは、決勝のステージを観に来てほしい……\n聴いてほしい歌があるって、しつこくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My sister wanted me to come see her performance at the finals…\nShe said there was a song she wanted me to hear‚ she kept asking me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.4806575057,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "私はただ、お姉ちゃんと一緒にいたいだけなのに……\nこの気持ちを分かってくれないのが悔しくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I just wanted to be with her…\nBut she didn't understand how I felt‚ and it frustrated me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.9806575057,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagaseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "nagaseliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.1900694248
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "それでつい\nお姉ちゃんなんていなければ良かったのに、って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then I ended up saying…\n\"I wish you weren't even my sister\"…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.9806575057,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagasektnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagasektnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 100.0599322356
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagasektnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagasektnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 100.0599322356
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてあんなこと言っちゃったんだろう\nあれがお姉ちゃんとの最後の会話になるなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why did I say that?\nThat was my last conversation with her…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.2806569971,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagasektnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagasektnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 111.7010432916
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "謝りたくても、もう謝れないんだよ\n私はどうしたらいいの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to apologize‚ but I can't anymore.\nWhat am I supposed to do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.0473236637,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagasektnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagasektnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 120.9630376694
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "（泣いてる琴乃ちゃんに私は何も出来なかった）\n（琴乃ちゃんの味方になるって麻奈さんと約束したのに）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I couldn't do anything for Kotono-chan while she was crying.）\n（I promised Mana-san I'd be there for her.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.8666643778,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagasektnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagasektnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 133.6125350513
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん……ごめんね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan… I'm sorry…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.6125350513,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagasektnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagasektnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 138.027679455
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "どうして渚が謝るのよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are you apologizing‚ Nagisa…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.027679455,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagasektnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagasektnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 141.9161938942
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "そうだね……変だよね……ごめんね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're right… That's weird… I'm sorry…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.9161938942,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagasektnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagasektnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 148.6779079076
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ……\nうわああああぁぁぁ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sob…\nWailing",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.6181790427,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagasektnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagasektnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 157.545122476
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagasektnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagasektnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 160.0784491973
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "（琴乃ちゃん、泣き疲れて眠っちゃった……）\n（こんなに目を腫らして、毎日泣いてるのかな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Kotono-chan cried herself to sleep…）\n（Her eyes are so swollen… has she been crying like this every day…?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.7333493548,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagasektnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagasektnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 165.7333493548
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagasektnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagasektnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 172.6989018874
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "（私に出来ることはないのかな……）\n（琴乃ちゃんのために何か出来ることは……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Is there anything I can do…?）\n（Is there anything I can do for Kotono-chan…?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.0666816709,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagasektnroom-00-night.webp",
