      "text": "麻奈さんは、琴乃ちゃんに笑顔でいてほしいって\n思ってるはずだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sure Mana-san wanted you to be happy‚\nKotono-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 402.9999844866,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
